健康免責聲明 Health Disclaimer

本資料庫提供的營養數據（蛋白質含量、營養素缺乏風險、補充建議等）僅供一般教育和資訊參考，
不構成醫療建議、診斷或治療。

所有補充保健食品（B12、鐵、鋅、維生素D、Omega-3等）的使用，
請在醫師或營養師的指導下進行，尤其是孕婦、哺乳期、兒童及有慢性疾病者。

Nutritional data and supplement recommendations in this database are for general
educational purposes only and do not constitute medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.
Consult a qualified healthcare professional before making dietary changes or starting
supplements, especially during pregnancy, lactation, childhood, or with chronic conditions.
